marketing: Shell Gadus S4 OG Multi-Season is primarly designed for use in heavyly loaded open gear applications, and operations under Multi-Season conditions, in mining equipment, shovels, draglines and excavators in open cut operations. Shell Gadus S4 OG Multi-Season is based on Aluminium Complex soap thickener and high viscosity semi-synthetic base oil containing enhanced extreme pressure and antiwear chemistry.
